The word `GROUP` is a reserved keyword in both &quot;MySql&quot; and &quot;PostgreSql&quot;, and hence you need to rename your table to something else:
```
@Table(name = &quot;GROUP&quot;) // &lt;- change the name
public class Group {

    // ...
}
```
Generally, you&#39;d pay attention to naming tables and fields, and avoiding using reserved keyword of the underlying DB vendor.

Reference: [MySql Keywords and Reserved Words](https://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/8.0/en/keywords.html#keywords-8-0-detailed-G), and [PostgreSql Key Words](https://www.postgresql.org/docs/current/sql-keywords-appendix.html)

